    "name": {
      "zh": "KOMZ Rusak反射式瞄具",
      "en": "KOMZ Rusak reflex sight"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "Rusak",
      "en": "Rusak"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "由Kazan光学仪器厂在90年代中期制造的准直式瞄具，主要用于捕猎。可以安装在燕尾基座上，但只有在拆卸状态下才可以对瞄具进行调节。笨重、不舒适、不清晰且存在时差的画面——这的确是那个年代的产物。然而，这玩意儿怎么样也比机瞄好使。",
      "en": "A collimator sight manufactured by Kazan Optical-Mechanical Plant in the mid-90s for use on hunting weapons. Installed on the Dovetail type rail, adjustment only possible after full disassembly. Heavy, uncomfortable, foggy sight with horrible parallax - a real product of its time. However, it's still slightly more effective than shooting with iron sights."
    },
